{"title":"Specialized: Disrupt the Decay – Chisel LTD Frameset in Earth, Wind, Fire, and Water","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/02/specialized-disrupt-the-decay-chisel-ltd-frameset-in-earth-wind-fire-and-water/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=specialized-disrupt-the-decay-chisel-ltd-frameset-in-earth-wind-fire-and-water","date":1614008998000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-206095\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"Specialized: Disrupt the Decay – Chisel LTD Frameset in Earth, Wind, Fire, and Water\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/SpecializedChisel.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>The Chisel is an XC hardtail and perhaps it’s this frame’s simplicity that inspired the designers at Specialized to develop a special edition pack, inspired by Earth, Wind, Fire, and Water. The pack is dubbed “Disrupt the Decay”.</p><p>Key Features:<br>-Frames come in as light at 1,400g<br>-D’Aluisio Smartweld technology from M5 alloy hydroformed tubes, which allows for fine-tuning of the ride qualities<br>-Progressive XC Geometry<br>-Internal cable routing<br>-BSA BB<br>-12x148mm spacing<br>-30.9mm Dropper post compatible</p><p>Available in June 2021. See more at <a href=\"https://www.specialized.com/us/en/chisel-ltd-frameset/p/199357?color=319089-199357&amp;searchText=71721-7301\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Specialized</a>.</p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"d3142bc1c8e326369c971d1386234abc2d84e9572e0958ae523e235ef27d2064","category":"Cycling"}